Block of code which perform some task.
we can use this functions number of times in our code for the repetative tasks.


  1)
  #!/bin/bash       ###  function creating
 function myfun {
    echo "hi"
 }

myfun      # function calling
myfun
myfun


2)
#!/bin/bash     ###  function creating
  myfun() {
  echo "hi"
}
myfun     #  function calling
myfun
myfun


